Name: Cube Color
About the game: 'Cube Color' - a game in which you need to repaint more territory in the color of your cube. Compete against computer or friends who will take over the earth. Key features: - 4 locations - Beautiful graphics and nice sound! - Quick achievement - A game for two people for one keyboard!
